---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Pricing · AroraMSP"
  description="Fixed-fee Microsoft 365 consulting. Tenant Health Check at $1,500. Migration and rebuild projects from $4,500. You know the cost before work begins."
  page="pricing"
  canonical="https://aroramsp.com/pricing"
  ogTitle="Pricing - AroraMSP"
  ogDescription="Fixed-fee Microsoft 365 consulting. Tenant Health Check at $1,500. Migration and rebuild projects from $4,500. You know the cost before work begins."
>
  <section class="page no-center wrap">
    <div class="page-head">
      <div class="sec-label">03 · pricing</div>
      <h2>Fixed-fee projects. You know the cost before work begins.</h2>
      <p>Every engagement is scoped and priced upfront. You approve the cost in writing before any work starts. No hourly billing, no change orders, no invoices for work you did not explicitly approve.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="pricing">
      <div class="tier reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="tier-name">// audit</div>
        <h3>Tenant Health Check</h3>
        <div class="sub">A complete read-only audit of your Microsoft 365 tenant with a prioritized action plan, written in plain English for both technical and non-technical stakeholders.</div>
        <div class="price">
          <span class="amt">$1,500</span>
          <span class="per">· fixed fee</span>
          <span class="note">USD · delivered in 5 business days from access grant</span>
        </div>
        <ul>
          <li>Security posture and identity review</li>
          <li>Conditional Access and MFA gap analysis</li>
          <li>License utilization map by user and SKU</li>
          <li>Mail flow, DNS, and email security review</li>
          <li>Admin role and privileged access audit</li>
          <li>Prioritized findings document in plain English</li>
          <li>60-minute walkthrough call with your team</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-ghost">Start with an audit →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="tier featured reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="badge">MOST POPULAR</div>
        <div class="tier-name">// project</div>
        <h3>Migration or Rebuild</h3>
        <div class="sub">End-to-end Microsoft 365 migration or tenant rebuild. Scoped after the audit so the price reflects your actual environment, not a generic estimate.</div>
        <div class="price">
          <span class="amt">from $4,500</span>
          <span class="note">scoped after audit · most projects fall between $4,500 and $18,000</span>
        </div>
        <ul>
          <li>Everything included in the Health Check</li>
          <li>Full migration or clean tenant rebuild</li>
          <li>Security baseline and Conditional Access policies</li>
          <li>Intune device enrollment and compliance</li>
          <li>SPF, DKIM, DMARC, and MTA-STS enforced</li>
          <li>Configuration documentation you own</li>
          <li>Team training and handover session</li>
          <li>30 days of post-launch support</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Discuss your project →</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pricing-note">
      <b>Why fixed fees?</b> Hourly billing misaligns incentives. A slower consultant charges more. A faster one charges less. Fixed-fee projects mean I am motivated to scope accurately and execute efficiently, and you know your budget before you commit. If scope changes materially after agreement, we discuss it before any additional work happens, not after.
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
